data.title: Not Only Acting Expert, These 7 Actresses Born in 1994 Also Have Enchanting Looks to Refresh the Eyes
data.meta_description: Their faces often appear on television screens and they always successfully portray various characters with excellence, unexpectedly these actresses were born in the same year, which is 1994.
data.text:
Kapanlagi.com - Having stunning visuals and excellent acting skills, these beautiful actresses from South Korea always become the talk of the town. They have starred in many famous dramas and now they are among the top actresses who have many fans.

Their faces often appear on television screens and they always successfully portray various characters with excellence, unexpectedly these actresses were born in the same year, which is 1994.

So, who are these actresses born in 1994? Check out the details below!

1. Han So Hee

Han So Hee ©Instagram.com/xeesoxee

Beautiful actress born on November 18, 1994 in Ulsan City, South Korea started her acting career in 2017 in the drama REUNITED WORLDS. Continuing to spread her wings, from 2017-2019 she starred in several famous dramas such as 100 DAYS MY PRINCE and ABYSS. In 2020, she became the talk of the town thanks to her role as the third person in the drama THE WORLD OF MARRIED which was highly successful and watched by many people in various countries.

2. Bae Suzy

Bae Suzy ©Instagram.com/skuukzky

Starting her career as an idol, Suzy has now transformed into a top actress in South Korea. This beautiful woman, born on October 10, 1994, has starred in a number of famous dramas, one of which is VAGABOND that she played alongside Lee Seung Gi. With her captivating visuals and extraordinary talent, it's no wonder Suzy has become the ideal woman for many people.

3. Seo Eun Soo

Seo Eun Soo ©Instagram.com/jj_minii

The owner of a sweet smile born in Busan on March 2, 1994 is one of the famous actresses in South Korea. Always amazing viewers with various roles she plays, Seo Eun Soo has starred in a number of famous dramas including HOTEL DEL LUNA, THE SMILE HAS LEFT YOUR EYES, and many more. Not to mention the film ON YOUR WEDDING DAY which became a hit and attracted a lot of attention from viewers.

4. Krystal

Krystal ©Instagram.com/vousmevoyes

The beautiful figure born in San Francisco, California, America on October 24, 1994 has starred in a number of hit Korean dramas. Known as the ice princess because of her cold-looking face, the acting ability of Krystal is unquestionable. The younger sister of Jessica Jung also often appears as a model and Brand Ambassador for various famous brands with her captivating visuals.

5. Park Se Wan

Park Se Wan ©Instagram.com/pp__swan

The actress who started her career in 2016 by starring in the drama titled THE RED TEACHER is one of the beautiful and charming actresses. Born on September 24, 1994 in Busan, South Korea, she has starred in various famous dramas including NEVER TWICE and JUST DANCE. Sewan is also known for her acting as Kim Go Eun's ghost friend in the drama GOBLIN and as Kim Sejeong's friend in the drama SCHOOL 2017.

6. Lee Hye Ri

Hyeri Girls Day ©Instagram.com/hyeri_0609

The owner of the full name Lee Hye Ri is a beautiful actress born in Gonjiam-eup, Gwangju, South Korea on June 9, 1994. Starting her career as a member of the girl group Girl's Day, Hyeri now focuses on developing her acting skills and becoming an actress. She has also starred in famous dramas such as REPLY 1998, and acted in a series of dramas like MISS LEE and TWO COPS which are equally interesting to watch.

7. Park Hye Soo

Park Hye Soo ©Instagram.com/hyesuuuuuya

Park Hye Soo is known not only for her acting skills, but also for her beautiful voice. With her stunning visual, Park Hye Soo is like a complete package in the Korean entertainment industry. Portraying various characters in dramas, she always gives her all and receives praise for her outstanding acting. The lead actress in the drama INTROVERTED BOSS has also come to Indonesia to promote her drama titled YONG PAL!

Beautiful and talented, these actresses were actually born in the same year. So, who is your favorite actress?

Author: Safira Damayanti
